description: Classic Tacos was founded to make the best tasting and most authentic tacos. We specialize in having 15+ salsas that we hand crafted from past down family recipes. Hand made tortillas for all our delicious tacos and authentic entrees like Picaditas, Tostadas, burritos, tortas, quesadillas, and our daily special make any trip well worth it! Fresh made gourmet street food!
name: The Classic Taco
